title: Rockstar

description.plain:
The pop-rap “ROCKSTAR” by LISA is the lead single to her solo album, Alter Ego. The single mixes elements of hip-hop and electronic music to showcase LISA’s bold style.

Lyrically, the song is about LISA’s wealth, skills, and her affluent life, consisting of fortune and success. LISA also boasts about her talents such as influencing others, rapping, singing, and being multilingual.

The music video compliments the rich, electronic concept of the single, including cyberpunk scenery setting place in Bangkok, Chinatown and Yaowarat Road in Thailand. Most importantly, the video displays LISA’s outstanding choreography and fashion.
